libmpeg3: libmpeg3 (MPEG Streams Decoding Library)
libmpeg3:
libmpeg3: libmpeg3 is a versatile and high-performance library capable of 
libmpeg3: decoding both audio and video from many different MPEG formats. It
libmpeg3: allows advanced editing and manipulation of MPEG streams, including
libmpeg3: MPEG video, mp3 audio, ac3 audio, and MPEG streams.
